OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,FStormont's Education Minister has
OL,7,Fwarned school governors he will no
OL,8,Flonger permit them to ignore guidance
OL,9,Fon reducing uniform costs as he
OL,10,Frevealed a price cap is under
OL,11,Fconsideration.
OL,13,FPaul Givan said he does not favour
OL,14,Fgetting rid of school uniforms,
OL,15,Finsisting such a move would be a
OL,16,Fretrograde step, but he said he will
OL,17,Fbe taking steps this year to ensure
OL,18,Fthey are more affordable.
