OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,FMr Givan said proposals due to go out
OL,7,Ffor public consultation later in the
OL,8,Fspring will include the beefing-up of
OL,9,Fcurrent departmental guidance by
OL,10,Fputting it on a statutory footing and
OL,11,Fthe introduction of a price cap on
OL,12,Funiform costs.
OL,14,FThe DUP minister was addressing the
OL,15,FAssembly during a debate raising
OL,16,Fconcerns about the impact of school
OL,17,Funiform costs on hard-pressed families.
