OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,FSinn Fein's motion proposed the
OL,7,Fintroduction of statutory guidance
OL,8,Fcompelling schools to ensure uniform
OL,9,Fcosts are kept affordable, while an
OL,10,Famendment tabled by the Alliance Party
OL,11,Fcalled for the introduction of a price
OL,12,Fcap.
OL,14,FResponding to the debate, Mr Givan
OL,15,Fsignalled his openness to both
OL,16,Fproposals.
OL,18,FThe minister also said he wants to
OL,19,Freview the criteria for accessing
OL,20,Fsupport grants to help families with
OL,21,Funiform costs.
