OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,FOn the potential for a price cap, Mr
OL,7,FGivan said: "There is no price cap in
OL,8,Fplace anywhere in these islands. That
OL,9,Fdoesn't mean we shouldn't do it. I
OL,10,Fbelieve it is something that we should
OL,11,Fbe looking at.
OL,13,F"And that's why it will be part of the
OL,14,Fconsultation that I will be putting
OL,15,Fforward in terms of the introduction
OL,16,Fof a price cap, because we do need to
OL,17,Flook at this issue."
OL,19,FThe minister voiced frustration that
OL,20,Fsome schools are not following his
OL,21,Fdepartment's guidance on uniform costs.
