OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,F"The current guidance makes it clear
OL,7,Fthat, in setting their uniform
OL,8,Frequirements, schools should ensure
OL,9,Fthey represent value for money and it
OL,10,Frecommends that schools enable uniform
OL,11,Fcosts to be as low as possible through
OL,12,Fminimising branded items and ensuring
OL,13,Fitems are available from a number of
OL,14,Fretailers.
