OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,F"And it is important to put on record
OL,7,Fthe fact that many schools have
OL,8,Ffollowed this guidance and I welcome
OL,9,Fthat. However, it also has to be said
OL,10,Fthat there are other schools which
OL,11,Fhave not. That is not a situation
OL,12,Fwhich I am going to permit to continue.
OL,14,F"Pending any longer-term decisions, my
OL,15,Foverarching aim in this area is to
OL,16,Fensure that all school governing
OL,17,Fbodies put affordability, comfort,
OL,18,Fsustainability and best value at the
OL,19,Fcore of their decision-making when
OL,20,Fthey set their school uniforms
OL,21,Frequirements.
