OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,F"I want to ensure uniform policies are
OL,7,Ftransparent and have been developed
OL,8,Fwith the input and support of parents
OL,9,Fand children.
OL,11,F"In doing so this has the potential to
OL,12,Fmake lives easier for both children
OL,13,Fand parents by reducing the burden of
OL,14,Fthe costs of attending school.
OL,16,F"We must ensure that the cost of
OL,17,Funiform is not a barrier to children
OL,18,Faccessing education."
