OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,FMr Givan said a pre-consultation
OL,7,Fexercise conducted by his officials
OL,8,Fhad highlighted a "wide variation" in
OL,9,Funiform policies between different
OL,10,Fschools.
OL,12,FHe cited the example of a girl's
OL,13,Fblazer at post-primary school level
OL,14,Fcosting #50 at one school and in
OL,15,Fexcess of #120 at another.
OL,17,F"The costs associated with uniforms
OL,18,Fshould never be a barrier to what
OL,19,Fschool you go to," Mr Givan added.
