OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,F"And sadly for some parents it is a
OL,7,Fconsideration that they're having to
OL,8,Ftake into account. I believe that's
OL,9,Fwrong and we need to make sure that
OL,10,Fthere isn't any barrier in place when
OL,11,Fit comes to what school you go to."
