OL,14,Fproposed his party's motion, said
OL,15,Ffamilies worst hit amid the cost-of-
OL,16,Fliving crisis are those most affected
OL,17,Fby the high price of uniforms.
OL,19,FHe said some schools have items on
OL,20,Ftheir required uniform lists that are
OL,21,F"totally unnecessary".
