OL,3,CPrice cap on school uniform costs to
OL,4,Cbe considered, Education Minister says
OL,6,F"Moreover, some schools, particularly
OL,7,Fbut not exclusively in the grammar
OL,8,Fsector, insist on branded PE clothing.
OL,9,FAnd this not only adds additional
OL,10,Fexpense, but also acts as a barrier to
OL,11,Fsome young people attending particular
OL,12,Fschools. Because parents know the cost
OL,13,Fof uniforms and PE gear would be
OL,14,Fbeyond their reach.
OL,16,F"Schools should be adopting a uniform
OL,17,Fpolicy that aims to make uniforms as
OL,18,Faffordable as possible and avoids
OL,19,Fexpensive add-ons."
